    <item>
      <title>国库在警告特朗普时正在像风险的资产一样进行交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/treasuries-suddenly-trade-like-risky-assets-in-warning-to-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在华尔街的岩石固定安全性，美国国债债券在恐慌时期一直是投资者的第一次征收港口。他们在9/11的全球金融危机期间集会，即使在美国自己的信用等级也被削减时。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/treasuries-suddenly-trade-like-risky-assets-in-warning-to-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Apr 2025 02:50:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着刺激，中国股票扩大了收益，Deal希望变得巨大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/chinese-stocks-end-three-day-winning-run-as-us-tariffs-hit-145</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国股票在第四天上升，因为人们期望对更强大的刺激，并希望最终达成的交易超过了对贸易紧张局势进一步升级的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/chinese-stocks-end-three-day-winning-run-as-us-tariffs-hit-145</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Apr 2025 01:49:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
